OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with occasional
OL,6,Frain. Some brighter spells for Orkney
OL,7,Fin the afternoon, but also a few
OL,8,Fshowers possible. Winds will be mainly
OL,9,Flight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy, but mostly
OL,12,Fdry evening. The rest of the night
OL,13,Fwill be largely cloudy, with a risk of
OL,14,Ffog developing for Shetland later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FPatchy mist and fog at
OL,17,Ffirst for Shetland. Otherwise mostly
OL,18,Fdry and bright, but rain and
OL,19,Ffreshening winds arriving from the
OL,20,Fsouthwest in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
