OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FAn
OL,6,Funsettled westerly pattern brings
OL,7,Fbright spells and scattered showers
OL,8,Fduring this period, with some sunshine
OL,9,Fat times but often windy.
